fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 declined 105.75 points or 0.56% to settle at 18,665.50. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, declined 2.70% to 11.24. Adani Enterprises, HDFC Bank, ICICI Bank were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The June 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 29 June 2023.
